span class=title> Re: What can we do to improve the message boards?</span><hr size=1> One thing that might help but take a bit of policing is kind of what they do on the EQtraders site but would need to wait tell new site with info goes live.<br>
<br>
Basicaly make a rule that if you have a question make sure to look for the answer on the site if you don't find it then come to the forum and ask.  This would cut down on newb question and some of the flack newbs might get (though I do sometimes like answering newb questions).<br>
