<br>
Another thing they do well there is that the moderators all have a link to the FAQ section of the site.  I think Whizbang had a similar link in his sig for a while.  The downside is that in their case they'd need to include their sig in every post, but the result will mean more chances for the truly new to find a place to start on the boards.  Sifting through pages of posts can be overwhelming, and I bet search just doesn't always get the results one craves.<br>
